est Tingz\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"3\" {{tba}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Bandit (song)|Bandit]]\"<br />{{small|(with [[Juice Wrld]])}}\n| 10<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8533646/lizzo-truth-hurts-number-one-seventh-week-hot-100|title=Lizzo's 'Truth Hurts' Tops Hot 100 for 7th Week, Tying for Longest Reign Ever for a Rap Song by a Female Artist|work=Billboard|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=October 21, 2019|accessdate=October 22, 2019}}</ref> || 6 || 4\n|11\n|\n* RIAA: Gold<ref name=\"RIAA\" />\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Dirty Iyanna\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/dirty-iyanna-single/1490639421|title=Dirty Iyanna - Single by YoungBoy Never Broke Again on Apple Music|website=[[iTunes]]|accessdate=December 13, 2019}}</ref>\n| 67 || 28 || 21\n|\u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Make No Sense\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.allaccess.com/urban/future-releases|title=Urban/UAC Future Releases|accessdate=January 13, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200113235522/https://www.allaccess.com/urban/future-releases|archivedate=January 13, 2020}}</ref>\n| 2020\n| 57 || 27 || 22\n|\u2014\n|\n| ''AI YoungBoy 2''\n|}\n\n===As featured artist===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of singles as a featured artist, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Fn Everything\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/fn-everything-feat-youngboy-never-broke-again-single/1343340033?ls=1&app=itunes|title=Fn Everything (feat. YoungBoy Never Broke Again) \u2013 Single by Damar Jackson|work=iTunes|accessdate=March 6, 2018}}</ref><br>{{small|(Damar Jackson featuring YoungBoy Never Broke Again)}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n| {{n/a|non-album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Untouchable Remix\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://genius.com/Yk-hundro-untouchable-nba-youngboy-remix-lyrics|title=Untouchable Remix (feat. YoungBoy Never Broke Again) \u2013 Single by YK Hundro|work=Genius|accessdate=July 22, 2018}}</ref><br>{{small|(YK Hundro featuring YoungBoy Never Broke Again)}}\n| ''Welcome to Hundroville'' EP\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Richer Than Errybody\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">([[Gucci Mane]] featuring YoungBoy Never Broke Again and [[DaBaby]])</span><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hypebeast.com/2019/9/gucci-mane-richer-than-errybody-nba-youngboy-never-broke-again-dababy|title=Gucci Mane, NBA YoungBoy & DaBaby Unite for \"Richer Than Errybody\" Single|work=Hypebeast|last=Montes|first=Patrick|date=September 13, 2019|accessdate=October 11, 2019}}</ref>\n| 2019\n| ''[[Woptober II]]''\n|}\n\n===Promotional singles===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of promotional singles, with selected chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:9em;\"| [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Billboard Hot 100|US]]<br/><ref name=\"US100\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs|US<br />R&B/HH]]<br/><ref name=\"Chart\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Solar Eclipse\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Solar Eclipse\" did not chart on the ''Billboard'' Hot 100, but peaked at number six on the Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles chart.<ref name=\"Bubbling\"/>}} || 46\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''Until Death Call My Name''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Right or Wrong\"<br/>{{small|(featuring [[Future (rapper)|Future]])}}\n| \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|}\n\n==Other charted songs==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"